---
title: Choc-Chip Blondies with Peanut Butter Caramel Drizzle | Serves 4+
description: Trust us when we say, these blondies are the bee’s knees of scrumptious desserts. Like a brownie, but not quite, these fudgey delights are studded with dark chocolate chips and finished off with a decadent gooey peanut caramel drizzled all over. Proceed with caution – these bad boys are addictive!

*Nutritional information is based on 8-10 servings*
